New Zone Harnesses & Link PAS



Women's Zone Harness




Shop Now





Zone Harness




Shop Now





Link Personal Anchor System




Shop Now









ZONE HARNESS
Built for routes that require maximum focus and minimum weight, the Zone harness is a high performance, sport climbing workhorse with Fusion Comfort Technology and other features tailor-made for hard redpoints. The Women's Zone is specifically designed for the shape and rise of a woman’s body.


SHOP NOW





 














QC Lab
From the Archives
How dangerous is a rope-worn carabiner? Can a hot belay device melt my anchor sling? What’s the strongest rappel knot? Learn the answer to these questions and more in our QC Lab archive—an in-depth collection of questions, reports and experiments from our quality assurance lab.


LEARN MORE













