 Welcome to Black Diamond Engineering, distributor of electro-mechanical based components and devices from trusted manufacturers. You can rely on Black Diamond for a wide selection of standard and customized products for your specific applications. All of our lines are known for crafting high levels of quality to exacting requirements. Your needs will be answered with value-added, cost-saving solutions. And with distribution centers in both the U. S. and Canada, we ensure delivery that’s on time every time



