Help Where You Need It.
Design & Engineering Services
Black Diamond’s engineering service group specializes in application assistance and product development. We use Pro/ENGINEER design software to create drawings and 3-D models that optimize the electro-mechanical design process.
Product Capabilities
Black Diamond supplies and manufactures a wide range of electro-mechanical products.  We handle both standard off-the-shelf products, as well as complete custom designs and modified standards, to meet your exact requirements.
Special Packaging
Our team is available to assist you with special packaging. To learn more about this service, please complete an inquiry form.










