Black Diamond Inc.


            
            Black Diamond, Inc. engages in design, manufacture, and marketing of outdoor equipment; and apparel for climbing, mountaineering, backpacking, skiing; and other outdoor recreation activities. Its brands include Black Diamond and PIEPS. The company was founded in 1989 and is headquartered in Salt Lake City, UT.

            
