BLACK DIAMOND PRODUCTSMechanical Components SpecialistsBlack Diamond is a North American based distributor of engineered electro-mechanical based components. A privately owned company, Black Diamond specializes in product selection for your specific application. This can be in standard catalog items or a custom solution when required.

We are partnered with some of the most respected names in the industry including Barry Controls, Dirak, Lee Spring and Vlier. These companies offer an extended standard product offering as well as custom design and manufacturing capabilities.

